modelVersions.name: V0.1
modelVersions.description:
日本の学校の体育館です。

This is a Japanese school gymnasium.

体育館の風景、体育館での式典、体育倉庫の3つの風景が描けます。

draw three scenes: a view of the gymnasium, a ceremony in the gymnasium, and the gymnasium warehouse.

背景絵の生成には使えますが、キャラクター絵の生成には向きません。めちゃくちゃ難しいです。

It can be used to generate background pictures, but it is not suitable for generating character pictures. It is very difficult.

1 体育館の風景　Scenery of gymnasium
taiikukan, stage, scenery, indoors, wooden floor,

1 体育館での球技風景 　Ball game in the gymnasium

taiikukan, indoors, multiple boys, 6+boys, sportswear, shorts, shoes, black hair, walking, sneakers, basketball uniform, multiple girls, standing, short hair, male focus,

2 体育館で卒業式とか式典　Graduations and ceremonies in gymnasiums.

shikiten, taiikukan, scenery, indoors, stage, flag,

床に敷物が引かれて卒業式とか式典モードになる。

3 体育倉庫　Warehouse in gymnasium

taikusouko, gymnastics mat, vaulting horse, scenery, indoors, wooden floor, window, shelf, box, ball, sunlight, day, basketball,
